We jointly modeled tissues together to detect age differences that were consistent across tissues, representing the main effect of age, as well as allowing an age-by-tissue interaction to capture tissue-distinct differences. We expanded the model in Eq. 1 to:3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
